          <div id="wwpID0E0JN0FA" class="List_Bullet_3"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span><span class="Hyperlink"><a href="../FAA5/Fleeing_Felon.html#wwpID0E0HK0FA" title=".05 Fleeing Felon">Fleeing Felon</a></span> (FE Jobs Referral Code)</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0IN0FA" class="List_Bullet_3"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span><span class="Hyperlink"><a href="../FAA6/Employment_Referrals_–_Hopi_Tribal_TANF.html#wwpID0E0HY0HA" title=".03 Employment Referrals – Hopi Tribal TANF">Referred Hopi</a></span> (RH Jobs Referral Code)</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0HN0FA" class="List_Bullet_3"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span><span class="Hyperlink"><a href="../FAA5/Referred_Mandatory.html#wwpID0E0JL0FA" title=".02 Referred Mandatory">Referred Mandatory</a></span> (RM Jobs Referral Code)</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0GN0FA" class="List_Bullet_3"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span><span class="Hyperlink"><a href="../FAA6/Pascua_Yaqui_Tribal_TANF_(PY‑YOEME).html#wwpID0E0KM0HA" title="06 Pascua Yaqui Tribal TANF (PY‑YOEME)">Referred Pascua Yaqui</a></span> (RT Jobs Referral Code)</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0FN0FA" class="List_Bullet_3"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span><span class="Hyperlink"><a href="../FAA5/Refugee.html#wwpID0E0WL0FA" title=".01 Refugee">Refugee</a></span> (RP Jobs Referral Code)</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0EN0FA" class="List_Bullet_3"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span><span class="Hyperlink"><a href="../FAA5/Victims_or_Survivors_of_Domestic_Violence__S.html#wwpID0E03J0FA" title=".06 Victims or Survivors of Domestic Violence, Sexual Harassment, Sexual Assault, or Stalking">Victims or Survivors of Domestic Violence, Sexual Harassment, Sexual Assault, or Stalking</a></span> (RB Jobs Referral Code)</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0DN0FA" class="Body_Text_3">&nbsp;</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0CN0FA" class="Body_Text_3">(See <span class="Hyperlink"><a href="../FAA5/JPPO_FAA_Procedures.html#wwpID0E0AT0FA" title=".01 JPPO FAA Procedures">JPPO FAA Requirements</a></span>)</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0BN0FA" class="Body_Text_3">&nbsp;</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0AN0FA" class="Body_Text_3">A Jobs referral may be needed for a new or renewal application or when a change is reported.  The following are the descriptions of different Jobs referral codes and directions regarding when to contact the DERS Helpdesk for referrals that show an error message in AZTECS:</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E06M0FA" class="Body_Text_3">&nbsp;</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E05M0FA" class="List_Bullet_3"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>When the first two digits under the JOBS CODE field on the WORW screen shows <span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold">any </span>of the following, the case is closed in the Jobs Program:</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E04M0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">03</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E03M0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">08</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E02M0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">19</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E01M0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">26</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0ZM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">30</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0YM0FA" class="List_Bullet_3"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>When the first two digits are 98 then the mandatory participant has been referred to the Jobs Program, no additional referral is needed.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0XM0FA" class="List_Bullet_3"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>When the first two digits show <span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold">any</span> of the following then the participants are already active in the JAS, no additional referral is needed:</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0WM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">00</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0VM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">01</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0UM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">02</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0TM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">10</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0SM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">12</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0RM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">14</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0QM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">18</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0PM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">22</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0OM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">23</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0NM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">24</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0MM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">27</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0LM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">50</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0KM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">53</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0JM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">54</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0IM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">55</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0HM0FA" class="Body_Text_3_Bullet">99</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0GM0FA" class="Body_Text_3">&nbsp;</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0FM0FA" class="Body_Text_3">When the case is closed in the Jobs Automated System (JAS), AZTECS displays the following message:</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0EM0FA" class="Body_Text_3">&nbsp;</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0DM0FA" class="Body_Text_3" style="text-indent: 0pt">“Client is Active in Jobs – Referral Not Created.”</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0CM0FA" class="Body_Text_3">&nbsp;</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0BM0FA" class="Body_Text_3">When this message displays in AZTECS and the Jobs Code field on the WORW shows a closed status code 03, 08, or 30, send an email to <span class="Hyperlink"><a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#bafeffe8e9f2dfd6cafedfc9d1fadbc0dedfc994ddd5cc" target="external_window"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="1a5e5f4849527f766a5e7f69715a7b607e7f69347d756c">[email&#160;protected]</span></a></span>.  Complete <span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold">all</span> of the following when sending the email:</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0AM0FA" class="Body_Text_3">&nbsp;</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E06L0FA" class="List_Bullet_3"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>Email Subject line: "JAS referral issue - Active in JAS"</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E05L0FA" class="List_Bullet_3"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>In the body of the email, include the AZTECS client ID and name of the participant.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E04L0FA" class="Body_Text_3">&nbsp;</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E03L0FA" class="Body_Text_3">DERS Help desk resolves the issue on the same day it is elevated.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E02L0FA" class="Body_Text_3">&nbsp;</div>
        </div>
