      <div id="page_content_container">
        <div id="page_content">
          <div id="wwpID0E0GIB0FA" class="Heading_Subject">CA Payment Standard (A1/A2)</div>
          <div class="WebWorks_MiniTOC">
            <div class="WebWorks_MiniTOC_Heading">&nbsp;</div>
            <dl class="WebWorks_MiniTOC_List">
              <dd>
                <div class="WebWorks_MiniTOC_Entry">
                  <a class="WebWorks_MiniTOC_Link" href="../FAA5/CA_Payment_Standard_(A1_2fA2).html#wwpID0E0DIB0FA">Policy</a>
                </div>
              </dd>
              <dd>
                <div class="WebWorks_MiniTOC_Entry">
                  <a class="WebWorks_MiniTOC_Link" href="../FAA5/CA_Payment_Standard_(A1_2fA2).html#wwpID0E0EHB0FA">Verification</a>
                </div>
              </dd>
              <dd>
                <div class="WebWorks_MiniTOC_Entry">
                  <a class="WebWorks_MiniTOC_Link" href="../FAA5/CA_Payment_Standard_(A1_2fA2).html#wwpID0E0DGB0FA">Legal Authorities</a>
                </div>
              </dd>
            </dl>
          </div>
          <div class="ww_skin_page_overflow">
            <table id="wwtabID0E0FIB0FA" class="Program_Grid" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" summary="">
              <tr style="vertical-align: middle">
                <td style="background-color: White; border-bottom-color: #FFFF00; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0.5pt; border-left-color: #FFFF00; border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 0.5pt; border-right-color: #FFFF00; border-right-style: solid; border-right-width: 0.5pt; border-top-color: #FFFF00; border-top-style: solid; border-top-width: 0.5pt; width: 71.75pt">
                  <div id="wwpID0EAAA0FIB0FA" class="Body_Text_Last_Revised"><span style="display: inline; text-indent: initial"><img class="Default" src="../FAA5/images/image2.png" width="100%" style="left: 0pt; max-height: 36px; max-width: 36px; top: 0pt" alt="Information on this page refers to the Cash Assistance program" title="Information on this page refers to the Cash Assistance program" /></span></div>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0EIB0FA" class="Body_Text_Public">The CA Payment Standard is used to determine the maximum CA benefit amount.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0DIB0FA" class="Heading_Section_Public">Policy</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0CIB0FA" class="Body_Text_Public">A1 and A2 are the two payment standards for CA which determine the CA payment level.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0AIB0FA" class="Heading_Sub_Public">A1 CA Payment Standard</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E06HB0FA" class="Body_Text_Public">The A1 standard is used when <span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold">any</span> of the following apply:</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E05HB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>When the budgetary unit has an obligation to pay a shelter cost, including <span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold">any</span> of the following:</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E04HB0FA" class="Body_Text_Bullet_Public">Homeowner association fees</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E03HB0FA" class="Body_Text_Bullet_Public">Mobile home space or taxes</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E02HB0FA" class="Body_Text_Bullet_Public">Mortgage</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E01HB0FA" class="Body_Text_Bullet_Public">Property taxes (residence or property)</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0ZHB0FA" class="Body_Text_Bullet_Public">Rent (residence or property)</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0YHB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>The participant is on a lease and residing in a housing unit subsidized by a local, state, tribal, or the federal government (i.e., public or subsidized housing).  Federal government subsidy includes credits or cash allowances.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0XHB0FA" class="Note_LBP"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.55in"><span style="font-style: normal; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline">NOTE	</span></span>The A1 payment standard applies regardless of whether a participant has any obligation to pay a portion of the rent.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0WHB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>The participant works in exchange for rent (in kind income).</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0VHB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>The participant has shelter costs paid by a third party for fewer than three months.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0UHB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>A participant in the military receives Basic Allowance for Housing (BAH).</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0THB0FA" class="Note_LBP"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.55in"><span style="font-style: normal; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline">NOTE	</span></span>Military allowances are shown on the Leave and Earnings Statement (LES) as additions and deductions.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0SHB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>The participant who has the shelter cost obligation is in foreclosure action, and the mortgage company accepts back payments.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0RHB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>The following do not require a shelter cost obligation:</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0QHB0FA" class="Body_Text_Bullet_Public">Kinship Care (KS) cases.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0PHB0FA" class="Body_Text_Bullet_Public">Kinship Foster Care (KF) cases.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0OHB0FA" class="Body_Text_Bullet_Public">Legal Permanent Guardian (LPG) cases.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0NHB0FA" class="Body_Text_Public">The annual A1 payment standard is 36% of the 1992 Federal Poverty Level (FPL).  (See the <span class="Hyperlink"><a href="../FAA6/A1_Payment_Standards.html#wwpID0E0MM0HA" title=".01 A1 Payment Standards">A1 Standard Table - CA</a></span> for the monthly payment standard.)</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0MHB0FA" class="Heading_Sub_Public">A2 CA Payment Standard</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0LHB0FA" class="Body_Text_Public">The A2 standard is used when <span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold">any</span> of the following apply:</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0KHB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>The budgetary unit is not obligated to pay shelter costs.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0JHB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>The shelter costs are paid on an ongoing basis by a third party for three consecutive months or more.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0IHB0FA" class="Note_LBP"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.55in"><span style="font-style: normal; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline">NOTE	</span></span>FAA uses the A1 payment standard when the participant is on a lease in a housing unit subsidized by a local, state, tribal, or the federal government.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0HHB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>The budgetary unit has an obligation to pay shelter costs but fails to provide verification of the cost.  (See <span class="Hyperlink"><a href="../FAA5/CA_Payment_Standard_(A1_2fA2).html#wwpID0E0EHB0FA" title="B CA Payment Standard (A1/A2)">Verification</a></span> for verification requirements.)</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0GHB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>The budgetary unit is not eligible for the A1 Payment Standard.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0FHB0FA" class="Body_Text_Public">The annual A2 Payment Standard is 23% of the 1992 Federal Poverty Level (FPL).  (See the <span class="Hyperlink"><a href="../FAA6/A2_Payment_Standards.html#wwpID0E0DM0HA" title=".02 A2 Payment Standards">A2 Standard Table - CA</a></span> for the monthly payment standard.)</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0EHB0FA" class="Heading_Section_Public">Verification</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0DHB0FA" class="Body_Text_Public">The obligation to pay a shelter expense for A1 must be verified when <span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold">any</span> of the following occur:</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0CHB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>New application when originally requesting CA or after a lapse in CA benefits </div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0BHB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>Three years from the date the expenses were last verified when the case is ongoing.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0AHB0FA" class="Note_LBP"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.55in"><span style="font-style: normal; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline">NOTE	</span></span>When the three-year period expires before the approval period ends, shelter expenses are verified at the next renewal.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E06GB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>A change of address is reported.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E05GB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>A change from A2 to A1 is reported.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E04GB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>Information is <span class="Hyperlink"><a href="../FAA6/Glossary_Terms_Beginning_with_Q.html#wwpID0E0S10HA" title="Q Glossary Terms Beginning with Q">questionable(g)</a></span>.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E03GB0FA" class="Heading_Sub_Public">A1 Verification</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E02GB0FA" class="Body_Text_Public">Verification that can be used for the A1 Payment Standard includes <span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold">any</span> of the following:</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E01GB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>Rent receipt</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0ZGB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>Landlord's statement</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0YGB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>Lease agreement</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0XGB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>Mortgage records, receipts, or payment booklet</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0WGB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>Housing assistance payments (HAP) contract or agreement</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0VGB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>Tax assessment notice</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0UGB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>Verification of Living Arrangements/Residential Address (FAA-0065A) form </div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0TGB0FA" class="List_Bullet_Public"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.25in"><span>●</span></span>Collateral contact to <span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold">any</span> of the following:</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0SGB0FA" class="Body_Text_Bullet_Public">Landlord</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0RGB0FA" class="Body_Text_Bullet_Public">Leasing agent</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0QGB0FA" class="Body_Text_Bullet_Public">Mortgage company</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0PGB0FA" class="Body_Text_Bullet_Public">Tax assessor's office</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0OGB0FA" class="Note_LBP"><span class="WebWorks_Number" style="width: 0.55in"><span style="font-style: normal; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline">NOTE	</span></span>Collateral contact can only be made to clarify documented verification or when the participant is unable to obtain the verification and asks for assistance.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0NGB0FA" class="Heading_Sub_Public">A2 Verification</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0MGB0FA" class="Body_Text_Public">Verification is not required to verify the A2 Payment Standard when the participant states they do not have an obligation to pay shelter expense.</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0DGB0FA" class="Heading_Section_Public">Legal Authorities</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0CGB0FA" class="Body_Text_Legal_Authorities">AAC R6-12-701</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0BGB0FA" class="Body_Text_Legal_Authorities">AAC R6-12-702</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E0AGB0FA" class="Body_Text_Legal_Authorities">AAC R6-12-703</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E06FB0FA" class="Body_Text_Legal_Authorities">AAC R6-12-704</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E05FB0FA" class="Body_Text_Legal_Authorities">AAC R6-12-705</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E04FB0FA" class="Body_Text_Legal_Authorities">AZ State TANF Plan</div>
          <div id="wwpID0E03FB0FA" class="Body_Text_Prior_Policy"><span class="Hyperlink"><a href="../Archived_Policy/Work_Registration_and_Program_Determination_2.html#wwpID0E0JG0FA" title="FAA5 Work Registration and Program Determinations">Prior Policy</a></span></div>
